        <title>【杂谈】三星平板使用实体键盘和手写笔输入法优化指北</title>
        <link>https://www.cherryswood.cloudns.ch/2024/%E6%9D%82%E8%B0%88%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%9E%E4%BD%93%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98%E5%92%8C%E6%89%8B%E5%86%99%E7%AC%94%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97/</link>
